Server Outline:
---------------
 * create a socket ( socket(2) ) 
 * bind the socket to a port ( bind(2) ) <--- most likely to fail
 * listen for new connections ( listen(2) )
 * loop :
   - look for a new connection
   - sleep


tcp       -  port number       16 bits
ip        -  ip address        32 bits
ethernet  -  ethernet address  48 bits
